messages.msgSnippet: Teresa, How fun!  Our Ethan is Feefon, too!  And feefers and feefer-do, freefree, feef and feefee (which my husband particularly hates, says it sounds like a
messages.messageBody:
Teresa,

How fun! Our Ethan is Feefon, too! And feefers and feefer-do, freefree,
feef and feefee (which my husband particularly hates, says it sounds like a
pink poodle name! LOL) When I call him me sweet baby boy, he gets this big
puffy chest and a stern look on his face and says, My not a BABY boy! My a
BIG boy! My a PERSON, MOMMY! I just love that he says MY instead of I...so
cute!

My poor kids have so many names, I'm sure they don't even know their true
full names. Hannah's name is Hannah Isabelle, but arund here she's Hannah,
Bella, Belle, Belly, Belly-Boo-Foo, Hannahbelle, Hannie, Hanniebella...it
goes on from there....I have 5 other children, so I won't even continue!!
LOL

Jennifer
